                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9835" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1490</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1388 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破围&#183;智变&#183;创值：中国电建财务数智化转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Breaking Through, Smart Transformation, and Creating Value: the Digital and Intelligent Transformation Path of China Power Construction Corporation&#39;s Finance Department</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谷增军，韩思雨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东工商学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国电力建设股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国电建；财务数智化转型；财务共享；司库体系</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Power China; Financial Digital Intelligence Transformation; Financial sharing; treasury system</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">为应对全球化业务扩张的政策监管要求、数字基建浪潮中的掉队危机、万亿规模管理效率瓶颈等“三重围城”困境，中国电力建设股份有限公司（以下简称“中国电建”）深入贯彻落实国务院国资委《关于中央企业加快建设世界一流财务管理体系的指导意见》要求，以“创建世界一流智慧财务体系”为目标，系统推进财务数智化转型。在转型过程中，一方面，面对全球化扩张中政策法规复杂、合规风险高、规模管理效率瓶颈等难题，通过构建全球统一的智能合规平台与风险预警体系，实现跨境业务财务数据的实时贯通与自动稽核，突破集团发展围城；另一方面，通过构建财务共享服务、全球司库管理、智能决策支持的一体化数智平台，升级数字基座，驱动业务技术融合，实现传统财务向智慧财务的跃变；再者，通过应用RPA、智能核算、集中共享等技术，大幅提升运营效率，优化资金使用，精益成本管控，最终实现价值创造。本案例深入剖析中国电建财务数智化转型背景、转型历程、转型路径、转型效果及未来规划，以“为什么转型、如何转型、转型效果如何、未来展望”为主线，旨在使学生更加深入地学习和理解企业推动财务数智化转型的相关理论及运用要点，培养学生剖析企业财务数智化转型中的实践问题能力，促进学生对智能财务以及企业信息数智化的理解。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In response to the &quot;three-fold siege&quot; dilemmas of policy and regulatory requirements for global business expansion, the crisis of falling in the digital infrastructure tide, and the bottleneck of management efficiency at a trillion-scale, China Power Construction Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;China Power&quot;) has thoroughly implemented the requirements of the State-owned Assets Supervision and Administration Commission&#39;s &quot;Guiding Opinions on Central Enterprises Accelerating the Construction of-Class Financial Management Systems&quot;, aiming to &quot;create a world-class intelligent financial system&quot;, and systematically promoting financial digital transformation. In the process of transformation, on the one, facing the complex policy regulations, high compliance risks, and efficiency bottlenecks in global expansion, a global unified intelligent compliance platform and risk early warning system are constructed to achieve realtime connectivity and automatic auditing of cross-border business financial data, breaking through the siege of group development; on the other hand, by constructing an integrated digital platform of financial shared, global treasury management, and intelligent decision support, upgrading the digital base, driving business-technology integration, and realizing the leap from traditional finance to intelligent finance; moreover, applying RPA, intelligent accounting, centralized sharing, and other technologies, significantly improving operational efficiency, optimizing the use of funds, lean cost control, and ultimately achieving value creation. This deeply analyzes the background, transformation process, transformation path, transformation results, and future planning of China Power Construction&#39;s financial digital transformation, with the main line of &quot;why transform, how to transform, and what are the results of transformation&quot;, aiming to enable students to more deeply learn and understand the relevant theories and application points of enterprises promoting financial digital, and to cultivate students&#39; ability to analyze practical problems in the process of financial digital transformation of enterprises, and to promote students&#39; understanding of intelligent finance and the digital transformation of corporate.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业数字化转型理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">流程再造；业财融合；数据治理；财务共享，司库管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
